description.narrative: Six year partnership between Counties Manakau District Health Board and the Samoan National Health Service (NHS) to strengthen NHS governance, management and clinical services and to provide a medical treatment scheme (MTS). The MTS includes New Zealand based specialist treatment (Overseas Referral Scheme) and in country treatment (Visiting Medical Specialist Scheme).
